title: Chinese Restaurant Hangs Banner 'Celebrating the Epidemic in the U.S.'
description: Chinese state media confirmed on Wednesday the legitimacy of an image circulating online of a Shenyang, China, restaurant banner celebrating Chinese coronavirus deaths in the United States.
content:
